<h3>Limitation of indicators&nbsp;</h3>
<ol>
<li>GDP
<ol>
<li>non market activities not accounted for</li></ol></li>
<li>GINI
<ol>
<li>only income inequality&nbsp;</li></ol></li>
<li>GNH
<ol>
<li>generosity is one of the parameters</li>
<li>ignores gender equality&nbsp;</li></ol></li>
<li>HDI&nbsp;
<ol>
<li>unequal distribution of wealth ignored</li></ol></li>
<li>doughnut theory - leaving no one in the hole behind.
<ol>
<li>Inner circle - 7 socio economic parameters of basic need like food shelter clothing</li>
<li>Outer circle - environment - climate change, ocean acidification, extreme weather events .</li></ol></li></ol>
